These are Puzzles for 2x4 Level 1

.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-1-1::.
There 4 different types of food: mango, pepper, pomegranate, raspberry
4 different games are played: billiard, bridge, canasta, chess
1. the person playing bridge is on the left of the person playing billiard##1
2. the person eating mango is the person playing chess##1
3. the person playing canasta is on the right of the person playing billiard##1
4. the person eating pepper is on the left of the person playing chess##1
5. the person eating raspberry is on the left of the person playing billiard##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |      2      |   3    |    4    |
| Food          | raspberry | pomegranate | pepper | mango   |
| Game   | bridge  | billiard     | canasta   | chess |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-1-2::.
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: disco, country, funk, d&b
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: parkour, soccer, swimming, volleyball
1. the fan of d&b is the person who's sport is soccer##1
2. the fan of disco is on the far right##1
3. the fan of country is on the right of the fan of d&b##1
4. the fan of d&b is on the right of the person who's sport is swimming##1
5. the person who's sport is soccer is on the left of the person who's sport is parkour##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1      |      2      |    3    |     4      |
| Music-Genre   | funk | d&b | country | disco    |
| Sport   | swimming    | soccer      | parkour | volleyball |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-1-3::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: lemonade, mirinda, almond-milk, cola
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: crime, drama, mystery, time-travel
1. the person watching mystery movies is on the left of the person watching time-travel movies##1
2. the person drinking lemonade is the person watching crime movies##1
3. the person watching drama movies is on the far right##1
4. the person watching time-travel movies is on the right of the person drinking cola##1
5. the person drinking almond-milk is on the left of the person watching drama movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |    2    |      3      |       4       |
| Beverage         | lemonade | cola | almond-milk   | mirinda |
| Movie-Genre   | crime   | mystery | time-travel | drama         |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-1-4::.
There 4 different types of food: lime, mango, raspberry, grapefruit
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: basketball, sailing, surfing, tennis
1. the person who's sport is sailing is the person eating grapefruit##1
2. the person eating mango is on the left of the person who's sport is surfing##1
3. the person eating mango is on the left of the person eating lime##1
4. the person eating mango is on the right of the person eating grapefruit##1
5. the person who's sport is basketball is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |    2     |    3    |     4      |
| Food   | grapefruit | mango | lime  | raspberry      |
| Sport         | sailing | tennis   | surfing | basketball |

