.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-1-5::.
There 4 different types of food: cauliflower, cucumber, kiwi, pineapple
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: montecristo, game, oliveros, dunhill
1. the person eating cucumber is on the left of the person eating cauliflower##1
2. the oliveros-smoker is on the right of the person eating kiwi##1
3. the person eating pineapple is on the left of the dunhill-smoker##1
4. the game-smoker is on the right of the oliveros-smoker##1

.:: Answer ::.
|        |     1     |  2   |    3     |      4      |
| Food   | pineapple | kiwi | cucumber | cauliflower |
| Cigar    | montecristo       | dunhill | oliveros | game     |

