.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-1-7::.
The people have 4 different jobs:  analyst, social-worker, doctor, mechanic
4 different pets are kept: chinchilla, ferret, mouse, rat
1. the owner of the mouse is on the far left##1
2. the mechanic is on the far right##1
3. the doctor is on the far left##1
4. the owner of the ferret is on the far right##1
5. the social-worker is on the left of the owner of the rat##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1   |     2      |     3     |   4    |
| Job   | doctor | social-worker | analyst | mechanic  |
| Pet           | mouse | chinchilla | rat       | ferret |

