.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-1-8::.
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: soul, trance, pop, folk
The people use 4 different means of transport: car, quad-bike, tram, trike
1. the person driving the trike is on the right of the fan of trance##1
2. the person driving the trike is the fan of folk##1
3. the fan of trance is on the right of the fan of soul##1
4. the fan of pop is on the left of the person driving the quad-bike##1
5. the person driving the car is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |      1       |     2     |    3     |    4     |
| Music-Genre         | pop | soul      | trance | folk |
| Transport   | car          | quad-bike | tram     | trike    |

