2. the dutch is on the left of the person driving the airplane##1
3. the spanish is on the far right##1
4. the person driving the helicopter is on the left of the person driving the motorbike##1
5. the person driving the ship is on the right of the argentine##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |     2     |   3    |    4     |
| Nationality   | colombian    | argentine       | dutch | spanish   |
| Transport     | helicopter | motorbike | ship   | airplane |

