.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-1-10::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: cola, hot-chocolate, milk, sprite
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: rugby, baseball, ice-hockey, rowing
1. the person who's sport is rugby is on the right of the person drinking hot-chocolate##1
2. the person drinking milk is on the right of the person drinking cola##1
3. the person who's sport is rowing is on the left of the person who's sport is ice-hockey##1
4. the person who's sport is baseball is on the right of the person drinking milk##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |  1   |   2   |       3       |   4    |
| Beverage    | cola | milk  | hot-chocolate | sprite |
| Sport   | rowing | ice-hockey | baseball          | rugby    |

