2. the owner of the lizard is on the left of the fan of rock##1
3. the fan of country is the owner of the rabbit##1
4. the fan of country is on the left of the owner of the lizard##1
5. the fan of electronic is on the right of the fan of rock##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |   1    |   2    |   3    |    4    |
| Music-Genre   | country | classical  | rock | electronic   |
| Pet        | rabbit | lizard | rat    | hamster |

