.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-1-20::.
There 4 different types of food: zucchini, cranberry, lettuce, mango
The people use 4 different means of transport: boat, car, scooter, snowmobile
1. the person driving the boat is on the left of the person eating cranberry##1
2. the person driving the car is on the left of the person eating mango##1
3. the person eating zucchini is on the left of the person eating lettuce##1
4. the person eating mango is the person driving the snowmobile##1
5. the person driving the boat is on the left of the person eating cranberry##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |    2    |     3     |     4      |
| Food   | zucchini | lettuce | cranberry | mango   |
| Transport     | scooter  | boat    | car       | snowmobile |

 